Description_lang: As an agent of the Vizier, cycle through a variety of experimental potions to achieve a variety of unique effects.

description_blz.en_US: As an agent of the Vizier, cycle through a variety of experimental potions to achieve a variety of unique effects.
description_blz.es_MX: Como agente del Visir, pruebas un surtido de pociones experimentales para obtener una variedad de efectos únicos.

description_blz.ko_KR: 재상의 대리인으로서 여러 실험용 물약을 사용해 가며 독특한 효과를 누릴 수 있습니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 身為輔臣的密探，輪流使用各種實驗性藥水，觸發各種獨特效果。
